        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Resilient Defense Assistance Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Defense to utilize various funds and programs to contribute to military climate resilience, including by authorizing funding from the Combatant Commander Initiative Fund to be used for climate resilience of military installations and essential civilian infrastructure.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
